25#ifndef _SYS_BPLIST_H
26#define _SYS_BPLIST_H
27
28#include <sys/zfs_context.h>
29#include <sys/spa.h>
30
31#ifdef __cplusplus
32extern "C" {
33#endif
34
35typedef struct bplist_entry {
36 blkptr_t bpe_blk;
37 list_node_t bpe_node;
38} bplist_entry_t;
39
40typedef struct bplist {
41 kmutex_t bpl_lock;
42 list_t bpl_list;
43} bplist_t;
44
45typedef int bplist_itor_t(void *arg, const blkptr_t *bp, dmu_tx_t *tx);
46
47void bplist_create(bplist_t *bpl);
48void bplist_destroy(bplist_t *bpl);
49void bplist_append(bplist_t *bpl, const blkptr_t *bp);
50void bplist_iterate(bplist_t *bpl, bplist_itor_t *func,
51 void *arg, dmu_tx_t *tx);
52
53#ifdef __cplusplus
54}
55#endif
56
57#endif /* _SYS_BPLIST_H */
